<h1>About Wildlife Explorer</h1>
<p>This application catalogs animals, their habitats, and observations.</p>
<p>Data is generated using Faker (and optionally CSV/API sources) to simulate real-world data.</p>
<h2>ER Diagram</h2>
<pre>
erDiagram
    ANIMAL {
        int id PK
        string common_name
        string scientific_name
        text description
        string classification
    }

    HABITAT {
        int id PK
        string name
        text description
        string location
    }

    OBSERVATION {
        int id PK
        string observer_name
        text notes
        datetime observed_at
        int animal_id FK
    }

    ANIMAL_HABITAT {
        int id PK
        int animal_id FK
        int habitat_id FK
    }

    ANIMAL ||--o{ OBSERVATION : "has"
    ANIMAL ||--o{ ANIMAL_HABITAT : "inhabits"
    HABITAT ||--o{ ANIMAL_HABITAT : "includes"
</pre>
